om/news/20385|title=Emma Roberts Lands Starring Role in 'Scream 4'|website=Bloody Disgusting|access-date=2017-09-18|archive-date=2018-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825120915/https://bloody-disgusting.com/news/20385/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

