== 私人生活 ==
2009年2月，羅勃茲成為[[露得清|露得清]]的品牌大使。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stylenews.peoplestylewatch.com/2009/02/10/exclusive-emma-roberts-named-neutrogena-brand-ambassador/|title=Emma Roberts Named Neutrogena Brand Ambassador|date=2009-02-10|publisher=People|accessdate=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140130091225/http://stylenews.peoplestylewatch.com/2009/02/10/exclusive-emma-roberts-named-neutrogena-brand-ambassador/|archive-date=2014-01-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>羅勃茲也數次出現於《Teen Vogue》的最佳穿著名單，其中包括2007年6月、2008年9月、2008年12月以及2009年2月。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.teenvogue.com/search/query?keyword=best-dressed|title=Teen Vogue's Best Dressed list|publisher=Teen Vogue|accessdate=2013-05-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20110226130946/http://www.teenvogue.com/search/query?keyword=best-dressed|archivedate=2011年2月26日}}</ref>

2011年9月，羅勃茲開始在[[莎拉·勞倫斯學院|莎拉·勞倫斯學院]]就讀，但2012年1月時她因為專注於工作合約而將自己的學業先放在一旁。<ref name=onhold>{{cite web|url=http://www.lifeandstylemag.com/2012/01/emma-roberts-puts-college-on-hold.html|title=Life & Style Exclusive: Emma Roberts Puts College On Hold|publisher=Life & Style|accessdate=2014-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302151025/http://www.lifeandstylemag.com/2012/01/emma-roberts-puts-college-on-hold.html|archivedate=2012-03-02}}</ref>

==== 感情生活 ==== 

在2012年拍攝《[[成人世界|成人世界]]》期間與演員[[伊凡·彼得斯|伊凡·彼得斯]]開始交往。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/evan-peters-inspired-adult-world-role-emma-roberts-article-1.1613046|title=Evan Peters: Fiancée Emma Roberts encouraged me to take role in 'Adult World'|publisher=New York Daily News|date=2014-02-13|accessdate=2014-11-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214031213/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/evan-peters-inspired-adult-world-role-emma-roberts-article-1.1613046|archivedate=2014-02-14}}</ref> 

彼得斯宣布他與羅勃茲於2013年3月訂婚。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/526843/how-do-emma-roberts-and-evan-peters-really-feel-about-being-engaged-watch-now|title=How Do Emma Roberts and Evan Peters Really Feel About Being Engaged? Watch Now!|date=2014-03-31|work=E! News|accessdate=2014-10-27|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502194741/https://www.eonline.com/news/526843/how-do-emma-roberts-and-evan-peters-really-feel-about-being-engaged-watch-now|dead-url=no}} Peters at 00:05 of video: "We're just enjoying being engaged right now."</ref>

2013年7月，兩人在蒙特婁的旅館發生爭執並互毆<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/emma-roberts-arrested-for-hitting-boyfriend-evan-peters-8713315.html|title=Emma Roberts arrested for hitting boyfriend Evan Peters|publisher=London Evening Standard|date=2013-07-17|accessdate=2014-10-27|archive-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404014901/https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/emma-roberts-arrested-for-hitting-boyfriend-evan-peters-8713315.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，羅勃茲打斷了彼得斯的鼻梁，還把他打得充滿咬痕，因此遭到警方逮捕，而彼得斯則因為羅勃茲身上沒有明顯傷痕而沒被逮捕。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/emma-roberts-sports-bruises-evan-peters-fight-article-1.1402698|title=Emma Roberts shows badly bruised legs after domestic dispute with boyfriend Evan Peters|publisher=NY Daily News|date=2013-07-18|accessdate=2014-10-27|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105100826/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/emma-roberts-sports-bruises-evan-peters-fight-article-1.1402698|dead-url=no}}</ref>因彼得斯不願提告，羅勃茲在數小時後獲釋。<ref name="people2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20718088,00.html|title=Did Emma Roberts's Relationship with Evan Peters Turn Violent?|publisher=People|date=2013-07-17|accessdate=2013-07-17|first=Dahvi|last=Shira|archive-date=2016-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160930032527/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20718088,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>兩人稱此事件是「一個不幸的意外以及誤解」，並表示兩人會「互相合作去克服它」。 <ref name="people2013"/> 

從2014年3月開始，彼得斯與羅勃茲處於一段分分合合的關係，2016年5月兩人宣佈解除婚約。同年8月兩人復合。

2017年1月，羅勃茲宣佈她與彼得斯再度訂婚。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4089838/Emma-Roberts-confirms-betrothed-boyfriend-Evan-Peters-rocking-huge-ring.html#socialLinks|title=Re-engaged!Emma Roberts 'confirms' she is betrothed to on/off boyfriend Evan Peters once again by rocking huge ring|date=2017-01-05|work=DailyMail|accessdate=2017-01-05|archive-date=2017-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208135739/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4089838/Emma-Roberts-confirms-betrothed-boyfriend-Evan-Peters-rocking-huge-ring.html#socialLinks|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年3月，確認兩人已再次分手和解除婚約。

自2019年起與演員[[蓋瑞特·荷德倫|蓋瑞特·荷德倫]]交往中。

